data.description: An Acre of landscaped, manicured land on a large corner lot overlooking the 18th Hole in beautiful Aspen Lakes Golf Course. Completely remodeled - this 4,250 sq.ft. home is stunning. Large Master with fireplace on the Main level. Gourmet Kitchen with Stainless Steel Appliances. Quaint and cozy Den fireplace. Office on the Main level. 2 additional bedrooms with ensuite bathrooms also on the Main Level. Big Bonus/Media/Game Room with full bathroom upstairs. Big, expansive windows look out onto the golf course and make this house light and bright. Private, Quiet and serene. Just a short drive to the beautiful town of Sisters, Oregon. Escape to Aspen Lakes, escape to Sisters, Oregon - this home has everything you need.
